
<h1> New story </h1>
<%= form_for @story do |f| %>
  <%= f.label :title %>: 
  <%= f.text_field :title %>

  <%= f.label :date_of_story_begining  %> 
  <%= f.number_field  :Order%>

  <%= f.label :url_optional_if_chaptered_story %>
  <%= f.text_field :url %>

  <%= f.submit %>
<% end %>

<p>use this form to upload stories to your site.
  
  to get the story URl got to google docs,file,publish to web, and then select the embeded option.

  the date will never be shown to readers, it is used soley to order stories by timeline.</p>
